body: "Add types/statuses/fields/seed-template counts to presets list rows. Keep backward compatible keys. Document in README that apply is idempotent (skips existing templates, deep-merges settings, --force to clobber, --dry-run preview), and that registerItemFields scalar fields (#97) cannot be set via pm create so seeds use built-in fields only."
